sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant Frontend
    participant FastAPI
    participant Algorithm
    participant Database

    Admin->>Frontend: Open Smart Dispatch page
    Frontend->>FastAPI: GET /admin/cases/pending
    FastAPI->>Database: Query pending cases
    Database-->>FastAPI: List of cases with coordinates
    FastAPI-->>Frontend: Cases list
    Admin->>Frontend: Select a case
    Frontend->>FastAPI: GET /admin/dispatch?case_id=X
    FastAPI->>Database: Get all verified NGOs
    FastAPI->>Database: Get active case counts per NGO
    FastAPI->>Algorithm: rank_ngos_for_case(lat, lon, ngos, counts)
    Note over Algorithm: Haversine distance score (50pts) + Caseload score (30pts) + Base (20pts)
    Algorithm-->>FastAPI: Ranked NGO list with scores
    FastAPI-->>Frontend: NGO rankings
    Frontend-->>Admin: Display ranked recommendations
